premise_source_doc_sentence: Sarah Elizabeth Huckabee Sanders  (  born August 13 , 1982  )  is an American political aide , currently serving as Principal Deputy White House Press Secretary .
She is the daughter of former governor of Arkansas and presidential candidate Mike Huckabee , and former Arkansas first lady Janet Huckabee .
